I'm not sure where this has come from, TBH. Paretha is a village (_"Ah, Paretha! Such a charming village"_ in Ezreal's Field Notes), Kumungu is a geographical area (Medarda Heirloom Map).

So they are not the same thing - however, Kumungu has yet to be *placed* on the map, so you can expect some cool new lore when we get there.

